Johto collects your personal information as reasonably necessary and proportionate to provide you with the Site and Services. Your personal information is used for the following specific purposes:
Provide the Services to you.
Provide notifications to you about your activity within the Services.
Provide customer support when you contact us to resolve any questions or issues.
